basic.description:
{Mysticism — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Regenerates 1 + 2 bonus = 3 spell points per day (plus natural daily recovery).

WOG Enhancement: +2 additional spell points regenerated per day at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Mysticism — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Regenerates 2 + 3 bonus = 5 spell points per day (plus natural daily recovery).

WOG Enhancement: +3 additional spell points regenerated per day at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Mysticism — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Regenerates 3 + 5 bonus = 8 spell points per day (plus natural daily recovery).

WOG Enhancement: +5 additional spell points regenerated per day at Expert level.

basic.description:
{Estates — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Generates 125 gold per day.

WOG Enhancement: Also generates hero_level × 5 additional gold per day (scales with hero level).

advanced.description:
{Estates — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Generates 250 gold per day.

WOG Enhancement: Also generates hero_level × 8 additional gold per day (scales with hero level).

expert.description:
{Estates — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Generates 500 gold per day.

WOG Enhancement: Also generates hero_level × 12 additional gold per day (scales with hero level).

basic.description:
{Learning — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero gains 5% more experience from all sources.

WOG Enhancement: Also passively gains 100 experience per day.

advanced.description:
{Learning — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero gains 10% more experience from all sources.

WOG Enhancement: Also passively gains 200 experience per day.

expert.description:
{Learning — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero gains 15% more experience from all sources.

WOG Enhancement: Also passively gains 300 experience per day.

basic.description:
{Navigation — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Movement over water increased by 30% (base 25% + WOG bonus).

WOG Enhancement: Navigation skill is more effective over water routes.

advanced.description:
{Navigation — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Movement over water increased by 55% (base 50% + WOG bonus).

WOG Enhancement: Navigation skill is more effective over water routes.

expert.description:
{Navigation — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Movement over water increased by 80% (base 75% + WOG bonus).

WOG Enhancement: Navigation skill is more effective over water routes.

basic.description:
{Sorcery — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Spell damage increased by 10%.

WOG Enhancement: Spell damage bonus increased to 15% at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Sorcery — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Spell damage increased by 20%.

WOG Enhancement: Spell damage bonus increased to 25% at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Sorcery — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Spell damage increased by 30%.

WOG Enhancement: Spell damage bonus increased to 40% at Expert level.

basic.description:
{Armorer — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Damage received reduced by 5%.

WOG Enhancement: Physical damage reduction increased to 8% at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Armorer — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Damage received reduced by 10%.

WOG Enhancement: Physical damage reduction increased to 13% at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Armorer — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Damage received reduced by 15%.

WOG Enhancement: Physical damage reduction increased to 20% at Expert level.

basic.description:
{Resistance — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

5% chance to resist enemy spells.

WOG Enhancement: Resistance chance increased to 10% at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Resistance — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

10% chance to resist enemy spells.

WOG Enhancement: Resistance chance increased to 15% at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Resistance — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

20% chance to resist enemy spells.

WOG Enhancement: Resistance chance increased to 30% at Expert level.

basic.description:
{Eagle Eye — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

40% chance to learn enemy spells (level 1-2).

WOG Enhancement: Can now learn level 3 spells at Basic level. Chance increased to 50%.

advanced.description:
{Eagle Eye — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

50% chance to learn enemy spells (level 1-3).

WOG Enhancement: Can now learn level 4 spells at Advanced level. Chance increased to 65%.

expert.description:
{Eagle Eye — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

60% chance to learn enemy spells (level 1-4).

WOG Enhancement: Can now learn level 5 spells at Expert level. Chance increased to 80%.

basic.description:
{Tactics — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero can rearrange troops in a 2-hex-deep zone before battle.

WOG Enhancement: Zone extended to 3 hexes deep at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Tactics — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero can rearrange troops in a 3-hex-deep zone before battle.

WOG Enhancement: Zone extended to 4 hexes deep at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Tactics — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero can rearrange troops in a 5-hex-deep zone before battle.

WOG Enhancement: Full tactical repositioning. Zone extended to 6 hexes deep.

basic.description:
{Scholar — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero can share level 1-2 spells when visiting or being visited by another hero.

WOG Enhancement: Can share level 3 spells at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Scholar — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero can share level 1-3 spells with allies.

WOG Enhancement: Can share level 4 spells at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Scholar — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero can share level 1-4 spells with allies.

WOG Enhancement: Can share any spell at Expert level, including level 5.

basic.description:
