Hero's sight radius increased by 1.

WOG Enhancement: Sight radius increased by 2 at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Scouting — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero's sight radius increased by 2.

WOG Enhancement: Sight radius increased by 3 at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Scouting — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero's sight radius increased by 3.

WOG Enhancement: Sight radius increased by 5 at Expert level.

basic.description:
{Pathfinding — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Reduces movement penalty on rough terrain by 25%.

WOG Enhancement: Penalty reduced by 35% at Basic level.

advanced.description:
{Pathfinding — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Reduces movement penalty on rough terrain by 50%.

WOG Enhancement: Penalty reduced by 60% at Advanced level.

expert.description:
{Pathfinding — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Eliminates all terrain movement penalties.

WOG Enhancement: Also grants +100 movement points on all terrain types.

